headline: Why Ralph Lauren (RL) Stock Is Down Today
summary: Shares of fashion brand Ralph Lauren (NYSE:RL) fell 3.6% in the afternoon session after new economic data intensified market agitation ahead of the Federal Reserve's policy decision later in the week.
